item.title: What does } else { Mean?
item.dc:creator: @chassy13 Chassy13
item.description:
@chassy13 wrote:

if (donator == 1) { sendMessage("You are a donator"); } else { sendMessage("You are not a donator"); }

If your donator value is 1, it will return the first message. If it is another number, it will return the second message. It basically means, “If donator does not equal 1”.
